                          DOpus CleanRAMDisk V1.0
                          ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
                 An AREXX script for cleaning your ramdisk.

                                     by
                              Roland Schwingel


@{" Introduction          " Link 0.}
